        "Minor in Sports Communication & Media": [
            "Minor in Sports Communication & Media The Minor in Sports Communication & Media provides students with sports-specific training in a variety of fields, including media relations, broadcasting, public relations, journalism, social media, new media, photography, advertising, radio, television, & film. It is an interdisciplinary program within the Ric Edelman College of Communication, Humanities, & Social Sciences. The Minor complements all of the majors within the college and many others across the university."
        ],
